Use this endpoint to enrich intent data for a company based on input values and return the desired output fields in the response.  Intent data is online behavior-based activity across the internet that links buyers and accounts to a topic. Key terminology includes:  Topics and categories - The Intent Enrich endpoint returns specific intent topics for a company based on your subscription. Multiple topics fall under a single category. Signal - Recent content consumption activity for a specific topic by people at a company Signal Score - Indicates a company's interest in a topic based on how recent content consumption compares to a historical baseline. Audience Strength - Indicates the size of the group at the company conducting research in this topic.
